title: Enter your weightings
insertText:
[Instruction for this page]

Please note that in order to progress the total must be 100%.

The CAM Tool provides a mechanism to relatively rank all Suppliers on the framework based on the information provided when applying to the framework.

It is the Buyer's discretion to determine how many Suppliers it wishes to take forward to the second stage of a further competition.
